details.excerpt: Nate Nash is the CEO of GovTribe, a company focused on taking open government data and making it useful for normal people. He is a continually learning Objective-C developer, an avid CrossFitter, and a massive fan of open government data. He can be found tweeting as @natenash203 and reachable via email at [nate@govtribe.com](mailto:nate@govtribe.com)
